originalText.text: My experience with Chas was truly spectacular. He made me feel extremely comfortable. I think I forgot where I was a few times. He worked so much tension out of my areas of discomfort and even gave me tips for relieving pain in those areas. Clear communication, attentive, and super friendly. I can’t wait to go back!

originalText.text: I had a wonderful time. I treated myself to a massage as an early birthday gift to myself and it was worth every penny. He made sure I was comfortable and to constantly check in which was really appreciated. He’s a great conversationalist. I just really enjoyed the experience overall. Totally recommend!

originalText.text: Magic hands and super knowledgable. Chas made me feel super cozy and relaxed. He definitely pulled out some unique moves to address my shoulders and it was immediately effective.  He also discovered a lot of my pain was actually my coming from my neck so he worked on releasing that. I personally like chatting and exchanging feedback on what works and what is too much during the massage and chas was cool with that. I tipped using venmo!
